## 3. SOC 2

### CC6 — Access Controls
Flag: missing MFA enforcement for admin accounts or privileged API operations
Flag: shared credentials or generic service accounts used across services
Flag: sensitive data not encrypted at rest — check Terraform resource configs, ORM model definitions
Flag: all users have equal access — no role-based access control implemented

### CC7 — Monitoring and Operations
Flag: no health check endpoint defined — /health, /readiness, /liveness
Flag: no structured logging or no correlation ID in log entries
Flag: no alerting configuration for authentication failures or error rate anomalies

### CC8 — Change Management
Flag: pipeline missing test execution before merge
Flag: no branch protection or CODEOWNERS configuration visible
Flag: infrastructure changes applied without pipeline enforcement

### A1 — Availability
Flag: no readiness or liveness probes in Kubernetes deployment specs
Flag: no graceful shutdown handler in application code
Flag: single point of failure with no replica or failover configuration

