## 8. NIST SSDF (SP 800-218)

### PO.1 — Security Requirements
Flag: SECURITY.md absent from repository root
Flag: no threat model or security architecture document referenced in project

### PS.3 — Protect Software Releases
Flag: container images not scanned before push — Trivy, Grype, Snyk Container
Flag: no SBOM generated in CI/CD pipeline — cyclonedx-npm, syft, cdxgen
Flag: build artifacts not signed or attested — Cosign, SLSA provenance
Flag: base image not pinned to digest — FROM node:20-alpine@sha256:<digest> required

### PW.4 — SAST Implementation
Flag: no SAST tool configured — CodeQL, Semgrep, Bandit (Python), Gosec (Go), SpotBugs (Java)
Flag: SAST not blocking merges on HIGH or CRITICAL findings

### PW.5 — Dependency Scanning
Flag: no SCA tool in pipeline — Dependabot, Snyk, OWASP Dependency-Check, pip-audit
Flag: dependency vulnerabilities not blocking merges

### RV.1 — Vulnerability Disclosure
Flag: no SECURITY.md with responsible disclosure instructions
Flag: no bug bounty or security contact defined

